                <div class="authority-kicker">Author</div>
                <div class="authority-name">Alex Thornton</div>
                <div class="authority-role">Backend Engineer with expertise in API security, token-based authentication systems, and microservices architecture for production applications.</div>
            </article>
            <article class="authority-card">
                <div class="authority-kicker">Reviewer</div>
                <div class="authority-name">Dr. Linda Park</div>
                <div class="authority-role">Security Researcher specializing in cryptographic implementations, JWT vulnerability assessment, and secure token lifecycle management.</div>
            </article>
            <article class="authority-card">
                <div class="authority-kicker">Trust Indicator</div>
                <div class="authority-name">950,000+ generated tokens</div>
                <div class="authority-role">All token generation is performed locally in the browser. No tokens or secrets are transmitted or stored on any server.</div>
