                    Configure the token parameters and click "Generate Token" to create a signed JWT.
                </div>

                <div id="errorDisplay" class="error-message" style="display: none;"></div>

                <div id="resultsDisplay" style="display: none;">
                    <div class="token-output">
                        <div class="token-output-label">Encoded JWT</div>
